description: From the leash around her neck, to the dirty wrinkled soles of her size fives, to her expressions of resignation, Blue Angel has clearly accepted her “position of submission” to an aristocratic domina! She humbly endures removing Mistress Sandra’s pantyhose with her teeth, having her nose squeezed by her owner’s strong red-polished size eights, and having her pretty lips pulled wide open by Sandra’s strong long toes as if her teeth are being inspected like those of a horse! And most intensely, Blue Angel’s grimy feet have to be cleansed by Sandra’s golden nectar, precious pee pouring long and steady onto her slave’s soles—naughty soles so filthy from walking around barefoot as Sandra’s human chattel! But Mistress Sandra is not totally cruel—after all, she does pop a few “treats” into Blue Angel’s mouth that suspiciously look like something any grateful doggie might enjoy! Crunch-crunch!!
title: Cutie Becomes a Slave
